<body>
<div class="mouse-spotlight" style="position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:99;pointer-events:none"></div>
<div class="deck">
  <div class="slide active" data-slide="1"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:520px;height:520px;top:-110px;right:-80px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.16"></div><div class="blob" style="width:300px;height:300px;bottom:-70px;left:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.12"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;top:38%;left:18%;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.10"></div></div><canvas class="particle-canvas" style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1" width="300" height="150"></canvas><div class="content text-center"><div class="text-[120px] mb-5 animate-[float_3s_ease-in-out_infinite] reveal" style="transition: opacity 0.35s, transform 0.35s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px);">🌱</div><h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(2.4rem,5.7vw,4.8rem)] font-black bg-linear-to-br from-accent-1 via-accent-2 to-accent-3 bg-clip-text text-transparent tracking-tight mb-4 reveal" style="transition: opacity 0.35s 0.08s, transform 0.35s 0.08s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px);">Benefits of the Project</h1><p class="text-[clamp(.9rem,1.4vw,1.2rem)] font-light text-text-muted tracking-[5px] uppercase reveal" style="transition: opacity 0.35s 0.16s, transform 0.35s 0.16s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px);">Smart process system for green hydrogen management</p><p class="mt-8 text-lg text-text-secondary max-w-4xl mx-auto reveal" style="transition: opacity 0.35s 0.24s, transform 0.35s 0.24s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px);">Detailed presentation for an engineering mini project on production, storage and transportation of green hydrogen using renewable energy sources.</p></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="2"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:340px;height:340px;top:-70px;right:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-40px;left:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Overview</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="card reveal"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">This project combines renewable energy input, hydrogen production estimation, storage management, transport tracking, alerts and report generation in one digital platform.</p></div><div class="card reveal"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">Its benefits extend across environment, economy, energy planning, industry, technology, education and policy support.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="3"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:360px;height:360px;top:-80px;left:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-40px;right:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Environmental benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="card reveal"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Cleaner energy pathway</h3><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Supports low-carbon hydrogen production using solar and wind energy.</li><li>Reduces dependence on fossil-fuel-based hydrogen processes.</li><li>Promotes clean energy use in industry and transport systems.</li></ul></div><div class="card reveal"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Sustainable development</h3><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Encourages efficient use of renewable resources.</li><li>Supports environmentally responsible industrial growth.</li><li>Builds awareness of long-term sustainable practices.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="4"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:360px;height:360px;top:-70px;right:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:230px;height:230px;bottom:-50px;left:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Environmental impact details</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4"><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl mb-2">🌍</div><div class="font-bold mb-2">Carbon reduction</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Green hydrogen can help decarbonize energy-intensive sectors and reduce greenhouse gas emissions when renewable electricity is used for electrolysis.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl mb-2">💨</div><div class="font-bold mb-2">Air quality</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Replacing fossil energy with cleaner hydrogen pathways can lower harmful local pollutants associated with conventional fuels.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl mb-2">♻️</div><div class="font-bold mb-2">Resource responsibility</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">The project encourages careful monitoring, which helps reduce leaks, wastage and unsafe operating conditions.</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="5"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:340px;height:340px;top:-70px;left:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-30px;right:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Economic benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="card reveal"><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Reduces long-term dependence on imported and volatile fossil fuels.</li><li>Improves renewable asset utilization, which can enhance investment value.</li><li>Digital monitoring lowers time spent on manual record keeping and supervision.</li></ul></div><div class="card reveal"><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Supports future jobs in hydrogen systems, software, data management and maintenance.</li><li>Encourages industrial modernization and green economy growth.</li><li>Creates a foundation for cost savings through better planning and reduced losses.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="6"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-70px;right:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:240px;height:240px;bottom:-40px;left:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Policy-linked economic value</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4"><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Mission support</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">India’s National Green Hydrogen Mission is designed to reduce fossil fuel imports and build domestic capability in hydrogen technologies.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Investment climate</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Projects like this improve readiness for future industrial deployment, research funding and pilot programs.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Skill development</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">The green hydrogen ecosystem encourages training, entrepreneurship and specialized technical jobs.</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="7"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-80px;left:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:230px;height:230px;bottom:-40px;right:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Energy benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4"><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl">⚡</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Efficient use</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Uses renewable electricity that may otherwise be curtailed.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl">🔋</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Storage</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Hydrogen acts as an energy carrier for later use.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl">🛡️</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Security</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Diversifies energy supply and improves resilience.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl">📉</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Lower waste</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Better monitoring reduces energy and process losses.</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="8"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:330px;height:330px;top:-70px;right:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-40px;left:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Industrial benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="card reveal"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Process management</h3><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Improves monitoring of hydrogen production values.</li><li>Supports tank-level availability and storage planning.</li><li>Provides clear dispatch and delivery records.</li></ul></div><div class="card reveal"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Operational efficiency</h3><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Reduces manual errors in production and transport logs.</li><li>Enables better scheduling and resource allocation.</li><li>Increases transparency in industrial workflow.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="9"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:340px;height:340px;top:-70px;left:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:230px;height:230px;bottom:-30px;right:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.06"></div></div><canvas class="particle-canvas-ambient" style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1" width="300" height="150"></canvas><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Technological benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4"><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Digital monitoring</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Converts a manual process into a structured software-based system.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Real-time data</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Supports quick updates and future live-sensor integration.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Dashboard analytics</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Shows energy input, production, storage and transport status in one place.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Alerts</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Warns users about threshold breaches or pending operational actions.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Reporting</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Generates records for academic review and management decisions.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Data management</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Stores information in a simple, searchable and maintainable database.</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="10"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-80px;right:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-40px;left:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Social benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4"><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl">🌿</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Cleaner surroundings</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Promotes cleaner industrial practices and awareness of sustainable fuel use.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl">🏥</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Health support</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Lower pollution exposure can contribute to improved public health outcomes.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl">📢</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Public awareness</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Makes renewable energy and hydrogen systems easier to understand.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-3xl">🙂</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Quality of life</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">A cleaner energy future supports safer and healthier communities.</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="11"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-70px;left:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-40px;right:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Educational benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="card reveal"><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Helps students understand green hydrogen production and management.</li><li>Demonstrates how renewable energy can be integrated with digital systems.</li><li>Connects engineering theory with a realistic software application.</li></ul></div><div class="card reveal"><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Improves skills in programming, GUI design, database creation and testing.</li><li>Encourages project-based learning, innovation and interdisciplinary thinking.</li><li>Creates a base for future research in AI, IoT and smart energy systems.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="12"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-70px;right:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-40px;left:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Government and policy benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4"><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">National mission alignment</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">The project supports India’s push to expand green hydrogen production, infrastructure and innovation.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Carbon goals</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">It reflects the type of digital support system needed to help decarbonization and clean energy planning.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="font-bold mb-2">Industrial transition</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">It encourages sustainable industrial development through digital monitoring and organized resource management.</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="13"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-70px;left:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-30px;right:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Future benefits</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-3"><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-2xl">📡</div><div class="font-bold mt-2 mini">IoT sensors</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Live pressure, temperature and flow data.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-2xl">🤖</div><div class="font-bold mt-2 mini">AI prediction</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Forecast production, demand and maintenance needs.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-2xl">☁️</div><div class="font-bold mt-2 mini">Cloud support</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Centralized remote access and backup.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-2xl">📱</div><div class="font-bold mt-2 mini">Mobile app</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Anytime monitoring and alerts.</div></div><div class="card reveal"><div class="text-2xl">🏙️</div><div class="font-bold mt-2 mini">Smart grids</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Integration with smart city and grid platforms.</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="14"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-70px;right:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:230px;height:230px;bottom:-40px;left:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Overall impact</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="card reveal"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">The project supports a cleaner environment by encouraging renewable-powered hydrogen production, better resource management and reduced process waste.</p></div><div class="card reveal"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">It also supports sustainable industrial growth through digital transformation, structured monitoring and smarter operational decisions.</p></div></div><div class="mt-6 card reveal"><p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">As an academic mini project, it shows how software engineering, energy systems and communication technologies can work together to solve future energy challenges.</p></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="15"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:500px;height:500px;top:-100px;right:-100px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.15"></div><div class="blob" style="width:300px;height:300px;bottom:-80px;left:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.12"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;top:40%;left:20%;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.10"></div></div><canvas class="particle-canvas" style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1" width="300" height="150"></canvas><div class="content text-center"><div class="text-[110px] mb-5 animate-[float_3s_ease-in-out_infinite] reveal">🚀</div><h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(2.3rem,5vw,4.2rem)] font-black bg-linear-to-br from-accent-1 via-accent-2 to-accent-3 bg-clip-text text-transparent tracking-tight mb-4 reveal">Why this project matters</h2><p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-4xl mx-auto reveal">This project is important because it brings together renewable energy, green hydrogen and digital monitoring in a practical system that can support cleaner energy management today and smarter industrial ecosystems in the future.</p><p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-muted tracking-[4px] uppercase reveal">Thank you</p></div></div>
</div>
